Challenges with Traditional IT Infrastructure as code 
Problem with traditional infrastructure - Terraform automation the updating or uploading new applications by GCP and Azure 
Iac tools  category configuration tool (ansible), server templating (docker)and provisioning tool (terraform)
Infrastructure as code - writing everything as code and making changes to code 

Terraform can used with all cloud providers even with vmware and physical machines 
Hashicorp configuration language (.tf)
Resource Blocks - block name (resource type) resource name
resource "local file" "pet" {
  filename = "/root/pets.txt"
   content = "We love pets!" }

resource "aws_instance" "webserver" {
     ami = "ami-0c2f25c1f66a1ff4d"
    instance_type = "t2.micro" }

terrafrom commands 
terraform init - to initiate (first then other commands )
terraform plan - display all the information + file is created 
terraform apply (type yes)- to apply and to confirm the build  {cat command is used to check file }
terraform show - to show all details that are created 

Update and Destroy Infrastructure
terraform ddestroy command 

A terraform file can have as many configuration file 
Terrafroms Basics - Start implementing basics commands 

















